The anticipated release from Ciara featuring Nigerian’s own Tekno was released this morning. She has released many successful collaborations that topped the charts, collaborations with Enrique Iglesias, Neyo, Missy Elliot and BOW WOW are examples. Ciara announced the release on her on Thursday via Twitter. For Tekno a Nigerian Afrobeat, RnB and hip-hop artist, this is not the first international collaboration. He has featured international artist Drake in his song, bad girl, released earlier this year. He sure is making waves with his talent. The collaboration has brought a mix of Afrobeat to her usual R and B genre. Enjoy! Read More: Davido Drops Much Anticipated “Nwa Baby” Read More: NBC Fines Radio Station For Airing Falz, Olamide, Wande Coal’s Songs 